Title: [ANN] ASSPACE TOKEN [ASP] - adultsocial.space - Crowdsale launch October 25
Body: |Decentralized social network|Crowdsale|White paper|Instagram|Twitter|Reddit|Telegram|   ASSPACE Team is building the new decentralized social network web application - adultsocial.space for IoP (Internet-for-Pleasure). Adultsocial.space is a platform intended to unite professionals with open-minded energetic, social, creative and curious youngsters in adult content production and give them both the same opportunities to produce content. Our project gives non-professionals to declare themselves and if they are able to interest take the jackpot.  Our goal is to build social network on the principles of decentralization with features that allowing to overturn the traditional adult content consumption. We are for the content adressed to a particular person and aspiration to receive freshiest content from performers with expected quality. Thus adultsocial.space offers crowdfunding collaboration with other Users. Adultsocial.space can be used as a "slightly" more advanced dating site.  All reward transfers inside application, any allocations and charges are implemented by ASSPACE Tokens (ERC-20 Ethereum Based Token). We offer something new in maintaining a constant social activity on adultsocial.space - stimulation any internal User activity by ASSPACE Tokens [ASP]. That means that posts, Likes, comments, broadcasts, content uploads, moderation, etc. will change in + or - Users ASP balance.  At first stage the platform will encourage Users with private amateur content. Next stage implementation of branded internal spaces for professionals of adult industry.   [ASP] ASSPACE Token Pre-ICO will be launched and will become available through a token crowdsale that starts October 25, 2017 .   Current Bonus 150% Pre ICO: 1 ETH = 2 500 000 ASP    To find out more about adultsocial.space and ASSPACE Tokens let us know by any channel how we can help you!  support@asspacetoken.com
